snippet: Serena Williams put the icing on the cake of another magnificent Wimbledon campaign by teaming up with sister Venus for a sixth doubles crown at the All England Club on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams put the icing on the cake of another magnificent Wimbledon campaign by teaming up with sister Venus for a sixth doubles crown at the All England Club on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Williams Sisters Win Sixth Wimbledon Doubles Crown
headline.main: Williams Sisters Win Sixth Wimbledon Doubles Crown
